'''布莱恩·理查德·威廉·布拉泽顿·霍华德'''（{{lang-en|'''Brian Richard William Brotherton Howard'''}}，{{bd|1983年|1月23日|catIdx=F}}），[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場_(足球)|中場]]，出身[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:南安普顿; zh-hk:修咸頓;}-]]青訓系統。

==球會生涯==

===南安普顿及斯温登===
霍华德出身於[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|南安普顿]]的青年軍，在2003年被放棄，期間沒有代表球隊上場。之後他到[[切尔西足球俱乐部|切尔西]]訓練<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/858124 |title=Chelsea Reserves 0 Southampton Reserves 1 |publisher=Chelsea F.C |date=7 April 2003 |accessdate=15 January 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116132903/http://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/858124 |archivedate=2014年1月16日 }}</ref>，球會向他開出一紙合約，但在他代表[[英格蘭20歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U20]]參賽期間，球會被[[罗曼·阿尔卡季耶维奇·阿布拉莫维奇|罗曼·阿布拉莫维奇]]買下並簽入多名頂級球員，霍华德選擇不在合約上簽字。之後他選擇加盟乙組足球聯賽（第三級）的[[斯温登足球俱乐部|斯温登]]，以獲得穩定的上場機會<ref name=Indy>{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/fa-league-cups/brian-howard-you-score-one-at-liverpool-and-everyone-knows-you-793197.html |title=Brian Howard: 'You score one at Liverpool and everyone knows you' |first=Ian |last=Herbert |newspaper=The Independent |place=London |date=8 March 2008 |accessdate=15 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140126035753/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/fa-league-cups/brian-howard-you-score-one-at-liverpool-and-everyone-knows-you-793197.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Howard's Way|url=http://www.thisisswindontownfc.co.uk/archive/2003/07/14/7312700.Howard_s_Way/|department=This is Swindon Town FC|newspaper=Swindon Advertiser|date=14 July 2003|accessdate=15 January 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116085709/http://www.thisisswindontownfc.co.uk/archive/2003/07/14/7312700.Howard_s_Way/|archivedate=2014年1月16日}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Swindon sign Howard|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/3065637.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=15 July 2003|accessdate=4 August 2013|archive-date=2003-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030814085114/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/3065637.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2003年8月9日主場對[[谢周三足球俱乐部|谢周三]]賽事中，他首次代表球會上場，以3-2落敗。他在10月1日對[[卢顿足球俱乐部|卢顿]]的比賽中打進個人職業生涯首個進球，在89分鐘助球隊追平<ref name=sb0304>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=35624&season_id=133 |title=Games played by Brian Howard in 2003/2004 |website=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116102530/http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=35624&season_id=133 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Swindon 2–2 Luton|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/3139868.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=1 October 2003|accessdate=4 August 2013|archive-date=2006-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060518195212/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/3139868.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。整個賽季他在各項比賽共上場41次並取得4個進球<ref name=sb0304/>。

在2004/05球季展開前，球會延長了霍华德的合約<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/3872449.stm |title=Robins duo extend contracts |publisher=BBC Sport |date=7 July 2004 |accessdate=15 January 2014 |archive-date=2004-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040714065503/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/3872449.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這賽季他擔任更多中中場的角色而非邊中場，這使霍华德本人感到滿意<ref>{{cite news|title=Howard relishing midfield role|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/4006659.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=12 November 2004|accessdate=4 August 2013}}</ref>。斯温登以中游位置完成聯賽，而霍华德在各項賽事共上場42次並打進6球<ref name=sb0405>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=35624&season_id=134 |title=Games played by Brian Howard in 2004/2005 |website=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116102534/http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=35624&season_id=134 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Swindon trio set to sit out games|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/4488911.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=27 April 2005|accessdate=4 August 2013}}</ref>。由於財政緊縮，球會不向他提供新合約<ref>{{cite news|title=Howard not offered Swindon deal|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/4546997.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=14 May 2005|accessdate=4 August 2013}}</ref>，他表示一支優秀球隊因財困而星散感到失望<ref>{{cite news|title=Howard's regret over Swindon exit|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/4562503.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=19 May 2005|accessdate=4 August 2013}}</ref>。

===巴恩斯利===
霍华德加盟[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|巴恩斯利]]，簽約兩年<ref>{{cite news|title=Tykes tie up treble swoop|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11713/2338064/|first=Mark|last=Buckingham|publisher=Sky Sports|date=2 June 2005|accessdate=4 August 2013|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305001421/http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11713/2338064|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由於腳部断骨而錯過首兩個月的比賽<ref>{{cite news|title=Howard blow for Tykes|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11713/2340904/|first=Alex|last=Livie|publisher=Sky Sports|date=5 July 2005|accessdate=4 August 2013|archive-date=2014-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116113029/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11713/2340904/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。復出後的他與中場搭檔[[斯蒂芬·麥克菲尔|斯蒂芬·麥克菲尔]]成為球隊爭取晉級[[英冠|英冠]]的重要成員<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/sport/football/other-clubs/sing-along-a-barnsley-howard-ready-to-go-down-in-history-1-2495904 |title=Sing-along-a-Barnsley! Howard ready to go down in history |newspaper=Yorkshire Post |date=1 April 2008 |accessdate=15 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116100652/http://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/sport/football/other-clubs/sing-along-a-barnsley-howard-ready-to-go-down-in-history-1-2495904 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，霍华德在晉級附加賽決賽因被侵犯而獲得自由球，其隊友從這自由球打進一球追平使比賽進入加時，最終擊敗[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|斯旺西]]晉級英冠<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2006/may/28/newsstory.sport1 |title=Colgan stop takes Barnsley up |first=Spencer |last=Vignes |newspaper=The Observer |place=London |date=28 May 2006 |accessdate=15 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116125322/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2006/may/28/newsstory.sport1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2007年3月，霍华德及另外兩名巴恩斯利球員被指控種族攻擊，最終被釋放<ref>{{cite news|title=Tykes trio released by police|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11713/2409399/|first=Tom|last=Adams|publisher=Sky Sports|date=26 March 2007|accessdate=4 August 2013|archive-date=2014-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116114847/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11713/2409399/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006/07球季，霍华德當選為球會年度最佳球員，而球隊亦保級成功。季後他簽下兩年新約<ref>{{cite news|title=Barnsley begin summer clear-out|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/barnsley/6642011.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=10 May 2007|accessdate=15 January 2014|archive-date=2007-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070908063825/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/barnsley/6642011.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2007/08球季，霍华德在[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]第五輪在93分鐘進球，以2-1淘汰[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]，並助球隊晉級至半決賽，不敵卡迪夫城而出局<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/7224063.stm |title=Liverpool 1–2 Barnsley |first=Chris |last=Bevan |publisher=BBC Sport |date=16 February 2008 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2009-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130031130/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/7224063.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/149268/Liverpool-stunner-a-painkiller-for-Brian-Howard |title=Liverpool stunner a painkiller for Brian Howard |first=Gideon |last=Brooks |newspaper=Daily Express |place=London |date=2 January 2010 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140118084542/http://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/149268/Liverpool-stunner-a-painkiller-for-Brian-Howard |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他當選為該球季最佳陣容<ref>{{cite news |title=PFA Championship Team of the Season |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11689_3469781,00.html |first=Joe |last=Drabble |publisher=Sky Sports |date=27 April 2008 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116114759/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11689_3469781,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2008/09球季季前傳出[[阿士東維拉|阿士東維拉]]、[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米德尔斯堡]]、[[愛華頓|愛華頓]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Kidd: We're not in talks with Everton over Brian Howard |url=http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/sport/kidd-we-re-not-in-talks-with-everton-over-brian-howard-1-2173265 |newspaper=Yorkshire Evening Post |date=3 March 2008 |accessdate=15 January 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116104746/http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/sport/kidd-we-re-not-in-talks-with-everton-over-brian-howard-1-2173265 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>和[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|谢菲尔德联]]有意羅致霍华德，而谢菲尔德联擁有者帕特里克·佳尼認為霍华德比隊中的[[迈克尔·汤奇|迈克尔·汤奇]]更為優秀，如果汤奇價值300萬至400萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，那麼霍华德就價值1,000萬英鎊<ref>{{cite news |title=£10m Howard is far better than Tonge |url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/football/barnsley/163-10m-howard-is-far-better-than-tonge-1-242574 |newspaper=The Star |location=Sheffield |date=21 May 2008 |accessdate=15 January 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116133541/http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/football/barnsley/163-10m-howard-is-far-better-than-tonge-1-242574 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，但主教練[[凯文·布莱克威尔|凯文·布莱克威尔]]否認對他有興趣<ref>{{cite news|title=Blackwell dismisses Howard move|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7410209.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=20 May 2008|accessdate=4 August 2013}}</ref>。

===谢菲尔德联===
2008年9月底，霍华德被外借至[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|谢菲尔德联]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Blades in Howard link|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11683/4206310/|publisher=Sky Sports|date=28 September 2008|accessdate=4 August 2013|archive-date=2014-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116114852/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11683/4206310/|dead-url=no}}</ref>至2009年1月，球會擁有購買權<ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7640074.stm | title=Blades sign Howard from Barnsley | publisher=BBC Sport | date=2 October 2008 | accessdate=3 October 2008 | archive-date=2008-12-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081204102322/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7640074.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。數天後以替補方式首次代表球隊上場，主場以3-0擊敗[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托尔城]]<ref>{{cite web | title=Taste of things to come | url=http://www.sufc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/PlayerFeatures/0,,10418~1414049,00.html | publisher=Sheffield United F.C | date=6 October 2008 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081007120112/http://www.sufc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/PlayerFeatures/0,,10418~1414049,00.html |archivedate=7 October 2008}}</ref>。

霍华德在谢菲尔德联有穩定的比賽機會，12月9日更打進在球會的首球，以1-0擊敗[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|诺丁汉森林]]<ref>{{cite news | title=Nottm Forest 0–1 Sheff Utd | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7763313.stm | publisher=BBC Sport | date=9 December 2008 | accessdate=10 December 2008 | archive-date=2008-12-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081211095125/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7763313.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。球會於2008年1月7日買下霍华德<ref>{{cite news | title=Blades complete Howard transfer | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7816545.stm | publisher=BBC Sport | date=7 January 2009 | accessdate=7 January 2009}}</ref>，而他亦助球隊獲得晉級附加賽，並在半決賽對[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯顿]]打進一球<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8034370.stm |title=Preston 1–1 Sheff Utd |publisher=BBC Sport |date=8 May 2009 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2009-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090512152042/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8034370.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在決賽以1-0不敵[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|伯恩利]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8060970.stm |title=Burnley 1–0 Sheff Utd |first=Paul |last=Fletcher |publisher=BBC Sport |date=25 May 2009 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2016-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113004944/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8060970.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===雷丁===
[[File:Brian_Howard_(cropped).png|thumb]]

雖然霍华德是在2009/10球季谢菲尔德联的先發陣容中，但他在9月2日以50萬英鎊轉會費加盟英冠的[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]，簽約三年，雷丁的[[詹姆斯·哈珀|詹姆斯·哈珀]]則被外借至谢菲尔德联<ref>{{cite news | title=Harper & Howard swap | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/8233734.stm | publisher=BBC Sport | date=2 September 2009 | accessdate=2 September 2009}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=Howard signs for Royals | url=http://www.readingfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1784707,00.html | publisher=Reading F.C | date=3 September 2009 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090905155256/http://www.readingfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1784707,00.html | archivedate=2009年9月5日 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

10月2日對[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|女王公园巡游者]]的打賽中他打進在球會首個進球，當時雷丁以4-0落後<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.readingchronicle.co.uk/sport/readingfc/articles/2009/10/20/42294-live--qpr-v-reading/ |title=LIVE – QPR v Reading |work=Reading Chronicle |date=20 October 2009 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116213513/http://www.readingchronicle.co.uk/sport/readingfc/articles/2009/10/20/42294-live--qpr-v-reading/ |archivedate=2014年1月16日 }}</ref>。11月28日對德比郡的賽事中受傷並缺席數個星期<ref>{{cite news|title=Reading FC's Brian Howard to have metal plates inserted into his jaw|url=http://www.getreading.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/reading-fcs-brian-howard-metal-4233094|work=Reading Post|date=30 November 2009|accessdate=16 January 2014|archive-date=2014-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116183123/http://www.getreading.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/reading-fcs-brian-howard-metal-4233094|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在足總盃第五輪對[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布罗姆维奇]]賽事中，在94分鐘完場前打進一球追和，[[吉尔维·西于尔兹松|吉尔维·西于尔兹松]]在加時的進球使雷丁自1927年來首次晉級至四分之一決賽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2010/feb/24/west-bromwich-albion-reading-fa-cup |title=Reading joy after breaking drought tempered by red card at West Brom |first=Richard |last=Rae |newspaper=The Guardian |place=London |date=24 February 2010 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116182425/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2010/feb/24/west-bromwich-albion-reading-fa-cup |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在季末，由於[[马修·米尔斯|马修·米尔斯]]停賽，他以隊長身份參加四場比賽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.getreading.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/brian-howard-looking-revenge-peterborough-4227718 |title=Brian Howard looking for revenge on Peterborough |work=Reading Post |date=15 April 2010 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116215241/http://www.getreading.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/brian-howard-looking-revenge-peterborough-4227718 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年9月對米德尔斯堡的比賽，霍华德因犯規而紅牌離場<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.readingchronicle.co.uk/sport/readingfc/articles/2010/09/20/48434-howard-suspended-after-royals-scrap-appeal/ |title=Howard suspended after Royals scrap appeal |work=Reading Chronicle |date=20 September 2010 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116211352/http://www.readingchronicle.co.uk/sport/readingfc/articles/2010/09/20/48434-howard-suspended-after-royals-scrap-appeal/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年3月中傳出他會重返南安普顿<ref>{{cite news|title=Howard committed to Royals|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11095/6829497/|publisher=Sky Sports|date=22 March 2011|accessdate=4 August 2013|archive-date=2014-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116182043/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11095/6829497/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但他留隊並在各項賽事上場28次，助球隊能參加晉級附加賽，但他並沒有在附加賽上場，而球隊亦在決賽不敵斯旺西<ref name=sb1011>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=35624&season_id=140 |title=Games played by Brian Howard in 2010/2011 |website=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116183932/http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=35624&season_id=140 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之後他表示如果在球隊無法得到足夠的比賽機會，他會偏向選擇離隊<ref>{{cite news|title=Howard: Play me or I'll leave Reading FC|url=http://www.getreading.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/howard-play-ill-leave-reading-4212611|work=Reading Post|date=9 June 2011|accessdate=16 January 2014|archive-date=2014-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116203011/http://www.getreading.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/howard-play-ill-leave-reading-4212611|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011/12球季上半季，他被外借至[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米尔沃尔]]三個月<ref>{{cite news|title=Millwall sign Reading midfielder Brian Howard on loan|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/15061950|publisher=BBC Sport|date=26 September 2011|accessdate=4 August 2013}}</ref>。他說他希望能在1月轉會窗重開時離開雷丁<ref>{{cite news|title=Howard set to leave Reading FC in January|url=http://www.getreading.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/howard-set-leave-reading-fc-4207270|work=Reading Post|date=8 November 2011|accessdate=16 January 2014|archive-date=2014-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116222632/http://www.getreading.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/howard-set-leave-reading-fc-4207270|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但沒有成事，在2012年6月約滿離隊<ref>{{cite news|title=Royals ring the changes|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11095/7723126/|first=Pete|last=O'Rourke|publisher=Sky Sports|date=4 May 2012|accessdate=16 January 2014|archive-date=2014-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116193613/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11095/7723126/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===朴茨茅斯===
霍華德在季前在[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|朴茨茅斯]]操練<ref>{{cite news |title=McLeod set to be among eight Pompey triallists |url=http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/sport/pompey/mcleod-set-to-be-among-eight-pompey-triallists-1-4059700 |first=Neil |last=Allen |newspaper=The News |place=Portsmouth |date=16 July 2012 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140117045908/http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/sport/pompey/mcleod-set-to-be-among-eight-pompey-triallists-1-4059700 |archive-date=2014-01-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，並在2012年8月16日與其餘九名球員簽下一個月合約<ref>{{cite news|title=Portsmouth announce 10 new signings on short-term deals|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19284581|accessdate=16 August 2012|publisher=BBC Sport|date=16 August 2012|archive-date=2012-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105150136/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19284581|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他被任命為隊長<ref>{{cite news |title=Appy goes Howard's way as skipper |url=http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/sport/pompey/appy-goes-howard-s-way-as-skipper-1-4177735 |first=Jordan |last=Cross |newspaper=The News |place=Portsmouth |date=18 August 2012 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140117045913/http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/sport/pompey/appy-goes-howard-s-way-as-skipper-1-4177735 |archive-date=2014-01-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。9月4日的[[英格蘭聯賽錦標|英格蘭聯賽錦標]]對[[般尼茅夫足球會|般尼茅夫]]賽事中打進一球<ref name=sb1213>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=35624&season_id=142 |title=Games played by Brian Howard in 2012/2013 |website=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140117182423/http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=35624&season_id=142 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但之後在一星期內兩次射失[[點球|點球]]後，他被解除主射點球的職務<ref>{{cite news |title=Pompey strikers to step up after skipper's spot of bother |url=http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/sport/pompey/pompey-strikers-to-step-up-after-skipper-s-spot-of-bother-1-4343230 |first=Jordan |last=Cross |newspaper=The News |place=Portsmouth |date=8 October 2012 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140117044403/http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/sport/pompey/pompey-strikers-to-step-up-after-skipper-s-spot-of-bother-1-4343230 |archive-date=2014-01-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2013年1月，霍華德及一眾球員得知不會獲得續約後離隊<ref>{{cite news |title=Harley heads list as quartet leave |url=http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/sport/pompey/harley-heads-list-as-quartet-leave-1-4654312 |first=Neil |last=Allen |newspaper=The News |place=Portsmouth |date=7 January 2013 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140117051421/http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/sport/pompey/harley-heads-list-as-quartet-leave-1-4654312 |archive-date=2014-01-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Portsmouth confirm six players have left the club|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21026466|publisher=BBC Sport|date=15 January 2013|accessdate=4 August 2013|archive-date=2013-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017061218/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21026466|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===布里斯托尔城===
2013年2月15日，霍華德簽約[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托尔城]]半年，穿11號球衣<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.co.uk/news/article/20130215-howardsigns-656736.aspx |title=Exclusive: Howard pens City deal |first=Adam |last=Baker |publisher=Bristol City F.C |date=15 February 2013 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329222856/http://www.bcfc.co.uk/news/article/20130215-howardsigns-656736.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在對[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]的賽事中以替補身份首次上場。他在季末不獲續約而離隊，效力期間共上場6次，全是替補身份上場<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.co.uk/news/article/20130508-retainedlist-813745.aspx |title=City announce retained list |first=Adam |last=Baker |publisher=Bristol City F.C |date=8 May 2013 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140117054025/http://www.bcfc.co.uk/news/article/20130508-retainedlist-813745.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===索菲亞中央陸軍===
2013年8月，霍華德轉投[[保加利亞足球甲級聯賽|保甲]]的[[索菲亞中央陸軍足球俱樂部|索菲亞中央陸軍]]，簽約一年<ref>{{cite news |title=Former Portsmouth midfielder Howard becomes first signing for CSKA Sofia side saved by English investment |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2395485/Brian-Howard-signs-CSKA-Sofia.html |first=David |last=Kent |newspaper=Daily Mail |date=16 August 2013 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2013-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021025205/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2395485/Brian-Howard-signs-CSKA-Sofia.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但因球會欠薪而在季中離隊<ref>{{cite news|title=Birmingham City midfielder Brian Howard glad to be back in England|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11694/9156080/championship-news-birmingham-city-midfielder-brian-howard-glad-to-be-back-in-england|first=|last=|newspaper=Sky Sports|date=8 February 2014|accessdate=14 February 2014|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222015531/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11694/9156080/championship-news-birmingham-city-midfielder-brian-howard-glad-to-be-back-in-england|dead-url=no}}</ref>，期間共上場13次<ref name=soccerway>{{cite web |url=http://int.soccerway.com/players/brian-howard/15978/ |title=Brian Howard |publisher=Global Sports Media |website=Soccerway |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140122014918/http://int.soccerway.com/players/brian-howard/15978/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===伯明翰城===
2014年1月，霍華德轉投英冠球會[[伯明翰城足球俱乐部|伯明翰城]]，簽約至季末<ref>{{Cite web |title=Howard homes in |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/2014014-howard-homes-in-1293479.aspx |publisher=Birmingham City F.C |date=14 January 2014 |accessdate=16 January 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116141314/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/2014014-howard-homes-in-1293479.aspx |archivedate=2014年1月16日 }}</ref>。他首次代表球隊是主場以2-0不敵[[约维尔足球俱乐部|约维尔]]<ref name=sb1314>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=35624&season_id=143 |title=Games played by Brian Howard in 2013/2014 |website=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=12 February 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140117190455/http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=35624&season_id=143 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月1日對[[德比郡足球俱乐部|德比郡]]的賽事中，他接應[[保羅·卡迪斯|保羅·卡迪斯]]的傳中打進一球先開紀錄，最終以3-3完場<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/288002/report |title=Sky Bet Championship: Birmingham City come back to grab 3-3 draw with Derby |publisher=Sky Sports |date=1 February 2014 |accessdate=2 February 2014 |archive-date=2014-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219010105/http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/288002/report |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===牛津聯===
2014年夏季霍华德不獲伯明翰城提供新約，直到9月15日才落實加盟[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[牛津联足球俱乐部|牛津聯]]，簽署短約至翌年1月，可延長至5月<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football-29207039 |title=Oxford United: Brian Howard signs for League Two side |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2014-09-15 |accessdate=2014-09-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150121184340/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football-29207039 |archivedate=2015-01-21 }}</ref>。2014年12月23日，霍华德被通知提前解約，期間只在聯賽上陣7場及足總盃上陣1場<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/30590790 |title=Brian Howard: Oxford United release forward |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2014-12-23 |accessdate=2014-12-24 |archive-date=2015-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109222921/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/30590790 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯==
霍华德曾代表[[英格蘭16歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U16]]至[[英格蘭20歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U20]]四個年齡階層的國家隊<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/england/mens-u20s/team/search?s=Howard |title=Brian Howard |publisher=The Football Association |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140118070846/http://www.thefa.com/england/mens-u20s/team/search?s=Howard |archive-date=2014-01-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><!-- not all player pages on the FA's website are accessible directly, without going through the search facility: Howard's is one such -->。由於霍华德的父親是蘇格蘭人，因此他能代表[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭]]參加國際賽，亦被蘇格蘭教練[[乔治·伯利|乔治·伯利]]徵召參加2008年3月26日對克羅地亞的友誼賽，但[[国际足球联合会|国际足球联合会]]認為他未在21歲前註冊代表蘇格蘭，因此不合資格<ref>{{cite news|title=Burley – No way for Howard|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11688/3295406/|first=Rob|last=Parrish|publisher=Sky Sports|date=13 March 2008|accessdate=16 January 2014|archive-date=2014-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140117170811/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11688/3295406/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霍华德曾上訴推翻国际足球联合会的決定但失敗<ref>{{cite news | title=Och aye the no, for Sheffield United ace | url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/sheffield-united/Och-aye-the-no-for.4789988.jp | newspaper=The Star | place=Sheffield | date=12 December 2008 | accessdate=16 January 2014 | archive-date=2013-06-16 | archive-url=https://archive.today/20130616074432/http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/sheffield-united/Och-aye-the-no-for.4789988.jp | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

